Conclusion
The U.S. wound care market is poised for significant growth, driven by an increasing focus on advanced wound care solutions and rising healthcare awareness. With the integration of innovative technologies and biologics, the market is set to deliver improved patient outcomes and enhanced operational efficiencies in wound management over the next decade.

